value.0: Though it seems to harbor no ill intent towards you, this strange creature has taken a definite interest in your belongings.
Pale and wispy, this ghostly dwarf bears a horrible gash down his left side. His entrails dangle from the broken bridge into the vast darkness below. The uniform he wears is all too familiar to you.
Worn by men and women in the King's service, this armor is intended for both battle and ceremonial use.
The Night Hag's pale green face emerges from the mists, a welcome sight after the perils of the Barrier. She seems ageless here, neither old nor young, only weary from her efforts on your behalf.
